room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Wands" by Mind Games in Roseau
room_description: Calling all muggles! Enrollment is open to the most famous school of witchcraft and wizardry. You have your acceptance letter, but when you arrive you learn that darkness has fallen on the school. Classes cannot resume until order has been returned to the castle. You won't be able to use magic to get yourself out. Spells won't work. Only brain power will help you puzzle your way out.
